Context:
For questions or inquiries related to course registration, withdrawal, deadlines, and course cost at George Brown College, contact the Coned registration team by completing the request form or using the following contact information:

Phone: 416-415-2000
TTY: 1-877-515-5559
Email: ask.george@georgebrown.ca

Students can also sign up for updates on application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, and tours by visiting the Social Media Hub. The information provided on this website is subject to change without notice and should not be considered as a representation or warranty. Students are responsible for verifying their own George Brown College fee requirements.
